posting_body: ['*2 Bed PLUS den or office*1 Bath* Single Family Home-Available September 1, 2022', 'Property Address', '1105 Woodbridge Street | St. Paul, MN 55117', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'Homes For Now |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'MAIN LEVEL-', 'Large living room and dining room with hardwood floors, spacious kitchen with ceramic tile, and 1 bedroom on this level.', 'UPPER LEVEL-', 'Spacious loft leading to 1 bedroom and full bathroom (bathtub & separate shower as well).', ' An additional room also on this level- perfect as a den or office (not a legal bedroom).', 'Washer and dryer in basement.', 'Near bus line, library, Rice Rec Center, and Wellstone Elementary.', 'Up to 2 pets ok-', 'we have the typical breed restrictions.', '*GARAGE NOT INCLUDED in rental, but some off-street parking is available.', 'Available Septenber 1, 2022.', '*Note, this property does NOT participate in the section 8 program.', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,460', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,416.00', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,416.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
